{"tid":1382311,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花］1823客戶服務主任致香港市民","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T19:39:04.000Z","uid":223378,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e1ac7601f52b0cc4c596fb02b34bce450f4dcf1","tid":1382311,"uid":223378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到高登有，我又無高登ac，就轉po過黎連登<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWanK7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWanK7a.png&h=624070c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先生/女士:<br />\n<br />\n你好，我們是一群1823客戶服務主任，負責接聽市民對政府22個部門的查詢及投訴，全年無休緊守崗位，擔當著市民與政府之間的橋樑。但眼見近期政府與警方的「不作不為」與「胡作非為」，以致手無寸鐵的普羅百姓慘被黑幫暴打凌虐，和平表達訴求的市民慘食無數無理的催淚彈、布袋彈與橡膠子彈而血濺街頭，同為服務市民的我們不齒與警隊為伍，決不做沉默一群，不作幫兇，要求政府立即回應市民五大訴求，包括成立獨立委員會嚴查警方濫權暴行！<br />\n<br />\n自上月起，香港市民發起一次又一次和平集會示威遊行，政府一次又一次漠視民意，繼而至本月二十一日元朗發生大規模恐怖襲擊，警方竟有如事不關己，只顧隔岸觀火，元朗及天水圍警署更落閘閂門袖手旁觀，助紂為虐，視人命如草芥。黑幫的無差別一鞭一棍不僅打至記者、小孩及孕婦等血流披面，亦令無數本以為打999可以求助的市民痛心疾首。身為香港的一份子，我們對警方連日多次失職與濫權感到極度失望，亦對特首林鄭月娥的「非人話」回應感到極其憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n身為香港政府另一服務市民的前線人員，我們1823客戶服務主任深明食君之祿，理應擔君之憂，即使簡單如一通電話或數秒留言，我們從不亦決不會因為政見不同而拒絕轉達市民意見。反觀受過專業訓練的紀律部隊&mdash;&mdash;警隊竟在市民命懸一線時視若無睹，袖手旁觀？甚至罔顧法紀，肆意將槍頭指向人民？試問警不守法，何以執法？難道你們已忘記服務市民的使命？難道你們已忘記自己也是香港人？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我們勢弱言輕，但決不虛作無聲！香港人，在民主自由的路上有許多同路人與你同在，請謹記不受傷、不被捕、不輕生、五大訴求、不撤不散，期待將來我們的路上仍然有你同行。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！<br />\n<br />\n1823<br />\n客戶服務主任們謹覆<br />\n2019年07月24日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/356m0FC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F356m0FC.png&h=e7fff6f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TR9WPyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTR9WPyX.png&h=c480a5fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pz5yRNi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPz5yRNi.png&h=e27375eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oeb99yZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeb99yZ.png&h=b79c22f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xh3kwNj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXh3kwNj.png&h=3b2d6fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEnENkF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEnENkF.png&h=04209983&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWCdRNm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWCdRNm.png&h=ee4927d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTFZNkG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTFZNkG.png&h=030baed0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu2tFFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu2tFFH.png&h=0df9847b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHLKYso.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHLKYso.png&h=5580fa74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23J4Ysu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23J4Ysu.png&h=f2501757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6iHK7u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6iHK7u.png&h=6db6d2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dq6FwNv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDq6FwNv.png&h=ba47ff06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0500c3f7f730bc1a7952577749e885129926e849","tid":1382311,"uid":223378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"4cb96cc30b7cefa3523bd129ccd57168494749a6","tid":1382311,"uid":223378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&